Dollars 348.9m.
Operating expenses, excluding restructuring and credit-related costs were
Dollars 171.6m, compared with Dollars 173.8m in the second quarter and
Dollars 191.7m a year ago.
Credit related expenses, including a Dollars 10.2m provision for loan
losses, were Dollars 44.8m, down from Dollars 96.3m in the 1991 third
quarter.
Non-accruing loans fell by 19.3 per cent to Dollars 759.8m or 7.84 per cent
of loans outstanding from Dollars 942m or 8.03 per cent a year earlier.
