Chicago, IL                   66,353               110.6
Atlanta, GA                   63,925               106.5
Minneapolis, MN               63,227               105.4
St Louis, MO                  60,081               100.1
STANDARD CITY, US             60,000               100.0
Houston, TX                   58,344                97.2
Phoenix, AZ                   55,718                92.9
Memphis, TN                   55,492                92.5
