unexpected 16 per cent decline in third-quarter net profit.
The company, which had projected a rise in results for 1991-1992 ending
December 31, said net profit in the three months to August 31 dropped to Fl
18.8m (Dollars 11.4m) from Fl 22.5m a year earlier. Sales were up 3 per cent
