to invest DM344m on a capital investment programme.
Last month, the UK Department of Trade and Industry cleared the sale of BP
Chemicals' 120,000-tonne-a-year low-density polyethylene unit in Antwerp to
Neste of Finland. It also sold its polyethylene film business at
Bromborough.
