<TEXT>
A SAME-DAY clearing system for Ecu securities will come into operation in
Paris at the start of next year, before the launch of a similar system
planned in the UK.
The creation of competing systems comes despite the downturn in the Ecu
market, which many investors now feel will revert to being a quiet backwater
of the Eurobond market.
